feel the same way.
- But I’m concerned.

515
00:32:34,718 --> 00:32:37,655
- You’re getting too close
too fast.
- That is none of your business.

516
00:32:37,655 --> 00:32:42,760
- You don’t understand.
- That’s because you aren’t
making any sense.

517
00:32:42,760 --> 00:32:46,497
