598
00:38:07,651 --> 00:38:10,287
♪ Where you are ♪

599
00:38:10,287 --> 00:38:14,191
♪ Come with me,
I’ll be where you are ♪

600
00:38:14,191 --> 00:38:16,994
I knew I was right about you.

601
00:38:16,994 --> 00:38:19,363
