620
00:39:15,018 --> 00:39:17,888
Did you kiss him back?

621
00:39:17,888 --> 00:39:19,389
No.

622
00:39:19,389 --> 00:39:21,592
Well, his lips were on mine,

623
00:39:21,592 --> 00:39:23,460
so I suppose so.

624
00:39:23,460 --> 00:39:27,598
What I mean is,
when he kissed you,
did you accept it?

625
00:39:27,598 --> 00:39:29,466
