629
00:39:50,287 --> 00:39:52,789
What the hell was that?

630
00:39:52,789 --> 00:39:54,758
I’m sorry.
I did not mean

631
00:39:54,758 --> 00:39:56,960
to be so quick about
revealing my secret to you.

632
00:39:56,960 --> 00:39:59,329
I suppose I just
could not resist.

633
00:39:59,329 --> 00:40:02,532
You truly have no idea

634
00:40:02,532 --> 00:40:04,668
you are the one.

635
00:40:04,668 --> 00:40:07,704
What the fuck
are you talking about?

636
00:40:07,704 --> 00:40:11,108
Like I said,
it’s really complicated,

637
00:40:11,108 --> 00:40:13,543
but you need to know the truth.

638
00:40:13,543 --> 00:40:15,679
