641
00:40:21,852 --> 00:40:23,587
your mind will not be able
to comprehend it.

642
00:40:23,587 --> 00:40:25,656
You said you wanted me to know.
Tell me.

643
00:40:25,656 --> 00:40:27,658
It’s more complicated
than just blurting the word--

644
00:40:27,658 --> 00:40:30,127
I don’t care.
You tell me the truth.

645
00:40:32,429 --> 00:40:34,064
I am a vampire.

646
00:40:36,166 --> 00:40:39,002
What? What?

647
00:40:39,002 --> 00:40:42,406
- What the hell
are you talking about?
- If you’ll let me explain--

648
00:40:42,406 --> 00:40:44,574
Like I said, it’s complicated.

649
00:40:44,574 --> 00:40:46,076
