651
00:40:47,978 --> 00:40:50,013
No...

652
00:40:50,013 --> 00:40:51,648
Shit.

653
00:41:15,706 --> 00:41:17,708
[vampires laughing]

654
00:41:17,708 --> 00:41:19,576
[howling]

655
00:41:20,911 --> 00:41:22,245
Whoo-hoo-hoo!

656
00:41:22,245 --> 00:41:24,281
- [howling]
- Yeah!

657
00:41:24,281 --> 00:41:27,117
- Burn, baby!
- [mutters]

658
00:41:28,485 --> 00:41:30,787
Did you take care of Paul?

659
00:41:30,787 --> 00:41:32,589
Would you expect anything less?

660
00:41:32,589 --> 00:41:35,392
It’s amazing
how some humans burn.

661
00:41:35,392 --> 00:41:37,761
I do not find that
the least bit comical.

662
00:41:41,131 --> 00:41:42,299
Sorry.

663
00:41:42,299 --> 00:41:44,401
Yeah. Sorry, Jasin.

664
00:41:49,940 --> 00:41:53,443
By the look on your face,
I can see that he didn’t
accept the truth.

665
00:41:53,443 --> 00:41:55,879
What makes you believe
I divulged anything to him?

666
00:41:55,879 --> 00:41:58,382
Oh, you slept with him.

667
00:41:59,883 --> 00:42:02,386
The way you’ve been going
on and on

668
00:42:02,386 --> 00:42:05,389
about this connection
that you have...

669
00:42:07,657 --> 00:42:09,593
You love him.

670
00:42:09,593 --> 00:42:13,663
And you told him,
didn’t you?

671
00:42:13,663 --> 00:42:15,332
I did.

672
00:42:15,332 --> 00:42:17,868
Let me guess.
He had the exact same reaction

673
00:42:17,868 --> 00:42:19,669
that Cassandra did.

674
00:42:19,669 --> 00:42:22,672
Cassandra accepted
the initial idea
of being with a vampire.

675
00:42:22,672 --> 00:42:26,243
It’s still unclear to me
as to what changed with her.

676
00:42:26,243 --> 00:42:28,111
What about Tara?
You were convinced

677
00:42:28,111 --> 00:42:30,814
that she was the one
before Caleb was even
in the picture.

678
00:42:34,117 --> 00:42:36,186
What happened?

679
00:42:37,554 --> 00:42:39,890
This decision is greater
than any other

680
00:42:39,890 --> 00:42:41,691
I’ve been forced to make.

681
00:42:41,691 --> 00:42:44,661
I must be sure
to choose wisely...

682
00:42:44,661 --> 00:42:46,363
with my heart.

683
00:42:46,363 --> 00:42:49,132
Are you sure that’s what
you’re choosing with?

684
00:42:49,132 --> 00:42:52,903
- What are you implying?
- Logan, you know that
Jasin is sincere.

685
00:42:52,903 --> 00:42:55,238
He’s not just thinking
with his dick.

686
00:42:55,238 --> 00:42:56,706
Let a vampire be in love.

687
00:42:59,209 --> 00:43:00,911
If he’s not,

688
00:43:00,911 --> 00:43:02,913
then we’ll all soon perish.

689
00:43:02,913 --> 00:43:04,848
I do not wanna think about that.

690
00:43:04,848 --> 00:43:06,183
He will make the right decision.

691
00:43:06,183 --> 00:43:07,784
Mind your own business,
both of you.

692
00:43:07,784 --> 00:43:08,919
I have been through this

693
00:43:08,919 --> 00:43:10,754
with him more times
than you can count.

694
00:43:10,754 --> 00:43:13,457
We’ve all been part of
this coven for many, many years.

695
00:43:13,457 --> 00:43:16,359
We stand behind Jasin
and his decision.

696
00:43:16,359 --> 00:43:17,828
Thank you for your loyalty.

697
00:43:22,232 --> 00:43:27,270
Caleb...is a phase.

698
00:43:27,270 --> 00:43:30,540
Tara’s the one
you’re supposed to be with.
You know that.

699
00:43:30,540 --> 00:43:34,911
I believe that decision
is left up to me,
is it not?

700
00:43:34,911 --> 00:43:36,713
