701
00:43:36,713 --> 00:43:39,649
I know how you feel
about Caleb.

702
00:43:39,649 --> 00:43:42,285
I know that you think
that he is the one.

703
00:43:42,285 --> 00:43:43,920
But how can you be sure?

704
00:43:43,920 --> 00:43:47,123
You’ve only known him
for a few days.

705
00:43:47,123 --> 00:43:49,759
Are you challenging me, Logan?

706
00:43:49,759 --> 00:43:52,195
I do not wanna die
because you can’t figure out

707
00:43:52,195 --> 00:43:54,664
who you wanna spend
eternity with.

708
00:43:57,033 --> 00:43:59,336
But I don’t have a choice.

709
00:44:03,273 --> 00:44:05,942
You created me,

710
00:44:05,942 --> 00:44:07,911
and I perish when you do.

711
00:44:07,911 --> 00:44:11,715
I agree that it is not fair,
but I did not write the rules.

712
00:44:11,715 --> 00:44:13,750
I am bound to them more so
than any of you.

713
00:44:13,750 --> 00:44:16,953
Then why don’t you just
make Tara one tonight?

714
00:44:16,953 --> 00:44:20,724
- She’s ready
to be turned, and--
- Enough discussion.

715
00:44:27,397 --> 00:44:29,432
Evening, boys.

716
00:44:30,333 --> 00:44:33,036
Did I come at a bad time?

717
00:44:33,036 --> 00:44:35,805
Everything is as it should be.

718
00:44:40,277 --> 00:44:41,978
How are you this evening?

719
00:44:41,978 --> 00:44:43,780
Come on, guys.

720
00:44:43,780 --> 00:44:46,516
