to the ends of the earth.

727
00:45:50,981 --> 00:45:52,515
Paul?

728
00:45:57,120 --> 00:45:58,755
Paul?

729
00:46:16,373 --> 00:46:18,008
[mutters]

730
00:46:18,008 --> 00:46:20,577
[clatter]

731
00:46:22,312 --> 00:46:25,081
