What the hell?

732
00:46:27,017 --> 00:46:30,120
Ow. Damn it.

733
00:46:30,120 --> 00:46:32,689
[Jasin]
I didn’t mean to startle you.

734
00:46:32,689 --> 00:46:34,724
And I’m sorry about the pot.

735
00:46:34,724 --> 00:46:38,161
I wasn’t sure
how to get your attention.

736
00:46:38,161 --> 00:46:42,599
Shouldn’t you be in a pile
of dust or something?

737
00:46:42,599 --> 00:46:45,802
You’d be surprised
how many myths are false.

738
00:46:45,802 --> 00:46:48,872
Like the myth
about vampires existing?

739
00:46:48,872 --> 00:46:52,242
Yes. Well, I can assure you,
that one is true.

740
00:46:52,242 --> 00:46:54,244
How’s that?

741
00:46:54,244 --> 00:46:56,246
Can we talk?

742
00:46:56,246 --> 00:46:58,982
Do vampires drink coffee?

743
00:46:58,982 --> 00:47:01,017
I would love some.

744
00:47:07,891 --> 00:47:10,093
I thought you said
you’d love a cup.

745
00:47:10,093 --> 00:47:12,629
I’m on my third already.

746
00:47:12,629 --> 00:47:14,331
I’m sorry.

747
00:47:14,331 --> 00:47:15,999
That is rude of me.

748
00:47:18,134 --> 00:47:20,136
